<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht II. und Heinrich XVI. von Schwarzburg, Herren von Leutenberg</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Unterstützung bei Freilassung des Wilhelm Ebner und anderer Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_381" id="190r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l29"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> den cʒweẏen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒum <expan>leuthemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> vnd auch <expan>g<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l30"><expan>Swarcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l31">daʒ Jr euch von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden ernſtlich darein geſecʒt vnd ſunderlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l32">den <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> vvılhelm cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> handen genomen vnd ew auch von ſeinen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l33">vnd ander der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen gnediglıch darẏnne beweiſet etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_381" id="190r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> den czweyen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czum
                                <expan>Leuthemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und auch
                            <expan>g<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> zu <expan>Swarczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Daz ir euch von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden ernstlich darein
                        geseczt und sunderlich den <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        Wilhelm czu <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> handen genomen und ew auch von
                        seinen und ander der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen gnediglich darynne
                        beweiset etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
